  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“They say it grows so cold up here in winter that a man’s laughter freezes in his throat and chokes him to death. Perhaps that is why the Starks have so little humor.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot448.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot448.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot448.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot448.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_4\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 4\">Chapter 4</a>, Eddard I, 48.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260407030156\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.006 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.007 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 79/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8424/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 302/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 25/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 456/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    3.891      1 -total\n100.00%    3.891      1 Template:Ref\n 65.69%    2.556      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:13584-0!canonical and timestamp 20260407030156 and revision id 217755\n -->\n",
